title: The Norn Crown
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

A model with //the Norn Crown// adds 6" to its synapse range. If the model does not possess the [[Synapse Creature]] special rule, it gains the [[Synapse Creature]] (6") and [[Shadow in the Warp]] special rules.

''Special'': Unlike other Tyranid Bio-artefacts, //the Norn Crown// does not replace a model's [[scything talons|Scything Talons]] and so can be taken in addition to any other weapon/upgrade.